  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "New 3D Golf Simulation: Harukanaru Augusta is a 1989 golf game by T&E Soft for the NEC PC-98 and the first in their New 3D Golf Simulation series of golf games. They ported it to the Sega Mega Drive in 1993. This version was not released outside Japan.\n\nThe game takes place at the Augusta National Golf Club and plays identically to Pebble Beach Golf Links.",
